
== To build

1. idlj -fall ChatService.idl
	(this will create the ChatService/ dir with generated files in it)

2. javac *.java


== To run

1. In a shell, start the orbd

  %   orbd -ORBInitialPort 1234 &

2. Start the server:

  %   java ChatServer -ORBInitialPort 1234

3. In other terminals, start as many clients as needed

  %   java ChatClient -ORBInitialPort 1234 localhost


